Sorry anon, but I no longer update like I used to. Now I just make the story in full before ever posting it. I feel like the chapter by chapter way I used to do it led to faster burnout due to a reliance on audience feedback.
But then I learned there is rarely ever feedback that goes beyond a simple "I like it" or "I don't like it" without either response delving any deeper.
So, I've decided not to let myself get bogged down by any of that and just wait to share anything when it's well and truly done.
